description:
A dusty old key that hasn't been used much. Opens most
of the prison cells in the Soreth Dungeon.
name: Prison Cell Key

description:
Dried blood stains the key. A peculiar mark is used to
signify its use to the blood chamber doors.
name: Blood Chamber Key

description:
An elaborate key used to open the main dungeon gates
of the Soreth Dungeon.
name: Soreth Dungeon Key

description:
Red, ripe, and juicy. It almost seems real if it were
not a toy.
name: Toy Tomato

description:
For all the necessary digging and rubble displacement.
Looks sturdy enough for tough work.
name: Shovel
